              "lines": [
                "### Strategic Insights\n",
                "\n",
                "**Growth Trajectory:** Strong 6x revenue growth from 2011-2014 peak, followed by sharp decline requiring investigation of market disruption or operational changes.\n",
                "\n",
                "**Category Strategy:** Bikes drive revenue (high transaction value) while Accessories drive volume (59.64% of customers). Strategic focus: Use Accessories for customer acquisition, cross-sell Bikes to maximize lifetime value.\n",
                "\n",
                "**Geographic Risk:** United States shows concentrated high-revenue performance. Diversification opportunity exists in underperforming regions (Canada, Germany, France) to reduce market dependency."
